title: Politics in Minutes (2016) (Epub) Gooner
description:
Politics in Minutes - 200 Key Concepts Explained in an Instant (2016) (Epub) Gooner

Publisher: Quercus Books (26 April 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1681444798
ISBN-13: 978-1681444796

Quick, accessible, compact guide to understanding key political concepts. Contents include: Liberty, Justice, Equality, Human rights, Social contract, Democracy, Monarchy, Anarchism, Capitalism, Socialism, Nationalism and Globalisation
